A cloud platform is needed in ABC Risk area to conduct end-user analytics on second-party data, with a majority of the data residing in an A3 bucket (i.e., without the need to copy it to the platform). Additionally, there's a requirement to avoid copying data to the ABC data lake, to link with ABC data. The chosen platform should have the capability, either native or through third-party tools, to implement fine-grained access control for business users.
